### Create integration job and payload
POST http://localhost:5001/api/orders/export-to-optimizer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "12345",
  "orderNo": "GC-2026-00125",
  "triggeredBy": "oktaycit@gmail.com",
  "forceReoptimize": false
}

### Read normalized export payload
GET http://localhost:5001/api/orders/12345/export-payload

### Save optimization result
POST http://localhost:5001/api/optimizations/result
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobId": "JOB-REPLACE-ME",
  "orderId": "12345",
  "optimizationRunId": "OPT-8891",
  "status": "optimized",
  "summary": {
    "totalSheetsUsed": 14,
    "totalWasteArea": 12.8,
    "efficiency": 87.4
  },
  "lineResults": [
    {
      "lineId": "12345-1",
      "optimized": true,
      "assignedBatchNo": "BATCH-01",
      "sheetCount": 4,
      "wasteArea": 2.1,
      "efficiency": 89.2
    }
  ],
  "files": [
    {
      "type": "cut-list",
      "name": "OPT-8891-cutlist.pdf",
      "url": "/files/OPT-8891-cutlist.pdf"
    }
  ],
  "message": "Optimization completed successfully"
}

### Query optimization result
GET http://localhost:5001/api/optimizations/OPT-8891

### Mark order as optimized in Herofis
POST http://localhost:5001/api/orders/12345/mark-optimized
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "optimizationRunId": "OPT-8891",
  "updatedBy": "system"
}

### Import Herofis CSV and build payloads
POST http://localhost:5002/api/herofis/import-csv
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filePath": "/Users/oktaycit/Projeler/CNCRevizyon/AI/GlassCuttingProgram/data/herofis/sample_herofis_import.csv",
  "encoding": "auto",
  "delimiter": "auto",
  "skipHeader": true
}

### Import Herofis JSON and build payloads
POST http://localhost:5002/api/herofis/import-json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filePath": "/Users/oktaycit/Projeler/CNCRevizyon/AI/GlassCuttingProgram/data/herofis/herofis_orders_20260411_151113.json"
}

### Fetch live Herofis/CamCAD order
POST http://localhost:5002/api/herofis/fetch-live-order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "oktaycit@gmail.com",
  "password": "camcad1",
  "orderNo": "10414",
  "baseUrl": "https://herofis.com",
  "verifySsl": false
}

### Update live Herofis status directly
POST http://localhost:5002/api/herofis/update-live-status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "oktaycit@gmail.com",
  "password": "camcad1",
  "liveOrderId": 3047885,
  "orderNo": "10414",
  "statusId": 20,
  "baseUrl": "https://herofis.com",
  "verifySsl": false
}

### Full live flow: fetch + optimize + save + mark + update Herofis status
### If targetStatusId is omitted, the API now defaults to 20 (Production).
POST http://localhost:5002/api/integration/herofis-live-optimize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "oktaycit@gmail.com",
  "password": "camcad1",
  "orderNo": "10414",
  "triggeredBy": "oktaycit@gmail.com",
  "baseUrl": "https://herofis.com",
  "verifySsl": false,
  "autoMarkOptimized": true
}

### Full live flow with explicit target status override
POST http://localhost:5002/api/integration/herofis-live-optimize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "oktaycit@gmail.com",
  "password": "camcad1",
  "orderNo": "10414",
  "triggeredBy": "oktaycit@gmail.com",
  "baseUrl": "https://herofis.com",
  "verifySsl": false,
  "autoMarkOptimized": true,
  "targetStatusId": 3
}
